---
title: Quick Mayo-Crumbed Chicken with Louisiana Roasted Potatoes & Smokey Aioli
description: You simply can't go wrong with crumbed chicken, roasted taters and a creamy smokey aioli to tie a meal together; and with only
four steps, this easy dinner will be ready in a flash.
